message.raw:
store joint damping coefficient for the model.

pass through kp_velocity to cfm damping in the range of (model damping, max allowed joint implicit damping).

calcualte force applied through implicit joint damping from kp_velocity (from the component of kp_velocity larger than model damping coefficient) and truncate the control force accordingly.
